highlights.text: “Woman” by Doja Cat is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 103 spots at #97.
Olivia Rodrigo has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “good 4 u” is the highest at #3.
“INDUSTRY BABY (feat. Jack Harlow)” by Lil Nas X and Jack Harlow is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #5.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 234 weeks straight.
